    <h1>Bulldog Care Guide</h1>
    <p><strong>Breed:</strong> Bulldog</p>
    <p><strong>Age:</strong> 8-10 years (average lifespan)</p>
    <p><strong>Size:</strong> Medium</p>
    
    <h3>General Care Tips:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Exercise: Bulldogs need moderate exercise to avoid overexertion due to their flat face.</li>
        <li>Diet: A balanced diet to avoid obesity, as they are prone to weight gain.</li>
        <li>Grooming: Minimal grooming needed but be sure to clean their skin folds regularly.</li>
        <li>Health: Regular vet visits to check for respiratory issues due to their brachycephalic face structure.</li>
    </ul>
    
